'''''Fire Hawk: Thexder - The Second Contact''''' (テグザー2 ファイアーホーク), also known as '''''Firehawk: Thexder 2''''', '''''Firehawk''''' or '''''Thexder II''''', is a video game developed and published by [[Game Arts]] for the [[MSX2]], [[MS-DOS]] and [[PC-8801]] in 1989 as a sequel to ''[[Thexder]]'' only in Japan. The MS-DOS version was later released by [[Sierra On-Line]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.org/stream/Sierra_News_Magazine_The_Volume_3_Number_3_Fall_1990_1990_Sierra_On-Line_US#page/n17/mode/1up |title=Sierra News Magazine, The - Volume 3 Number 3 - Fall 1990 (1990)(Sierra On-Line)(US) |year=1990 |accessdate=2015-11-07}}</ref>

